Dialogue: 9,0:12:35.25,0:12:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Vá!
Dialogue: 9,0:12:44.13,0:12:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,O que você está fazendo, Shinatose?
Dialogue: 9,0:12:46.84,0:12:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Você realmente descartou seu combustível?
Dialogue: 9,0:12:48.22,0:12:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 9,0:12:49.93,0:12:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Os Gauna reagem a Kabi\Nand partículas de alta densidade Heigus.
Dialogue: 9,0:12:54.68,0:12:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,O que?
Dialogue: 9,0:12:58.52,0:12:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Olhe!
Dialogue: 9,0:12:59.73,0:13:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Os Gauna pararam de nos seguir.
Dialogue: 9,0:13:15.79,0:13:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[T0]...[T1]Yeah...
Dialogue: 9,0:13:17.87,0:13:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}Mas sem combustível...
Dialogue: 9,0:13:20.58,0:13:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Há energia suficiente para operar\Nas asas de empunhadura, o que deve nos permitir navegar com a corrente do ar.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.12,0:14:01.07,100 Sights,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}100 Atrativos de Sidonia
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.12,0:13:58.07,100 Sights - Copy,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}Setor Administrativo, Rua Suja
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.07,0:14:01.07,100 Sights - Copy,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}Casa de Yure Shinatose
Dialogue: 9,0:14:21.31,0:14:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,HQ, qualquer mensagem de Izana?
Dialogue: 9,0:14:24.15,0:14:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Sem contato.
Dialogue: 9,0:14:26.65,0:14:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Não temos informações sobre o que aconteceu com eles após a entrada.
Dialogue: 9,0:14:35.03,0:14:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanikaze{**-san}, tenho certeza de que Izana{**-san} está bem.
Dialogue: 9,0:14:44.92,0:14:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Você está certa, Tsumugi.
Dialogue: 9,0:15:05.19,0:15:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Logo chegaremos aos últimos conhecidos locais de Izana.
Dialogue: 9,0:15:08.98,0:15:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Pronto para a entrada atmosférica!
Dialogue: 9,0:15:12.53,0:15:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Gauna direto à frente!
Dialogue: 9,0:15:16.82,0:15:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumugi, encerre a formação!
Dialogue: 9,0:15:37.30,0:15:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Impactos confirmados!
Dialogue: 9,0:15:38.72,0:15:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Formação!
Dialogue: 9,0:15:39.55,0:15:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Copiado!
Dialogue: 9,0:16:04.12,0:16:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Estão funcionando muito bem juntos.
Dialogue: 9,0:16:12.34,0:16:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,O que é isso, Tsumugi?
Dialogue: 9,0:16:14.21,0:16:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Posso sentir algo\Nprofundo na atmosfera.
