Dialogue: 9,0:17:07.14,0:17:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Ele caiu a uma velocidade muito alta.
Dialogue: 9,0:17:10.73,0:17:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Pobre Tanikaze.
Dialogue: 9,0:17:22.62,0:17:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,...{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}Tanikaze...
Dialogue: 9,0:17:24.12,0:17:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanikaze!
Dialogue: 9,0:17:25.29,0:17:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Responda.
Dialogue: 9,0:17:38.09,0:17:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,...{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}Tanikaze...
Dialogue: 9,0:17:39.59,0:17:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanikaze!
Dialogue: 9,0:17:40.80,0:17:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Responda.
Dialogue: 9,0:17:43.30,0:17:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Aqui!
Dialogue: 9,0:17:45.31,0:17:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,...{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}Estou viva...
Dialogue: 9,0:17:46.93,0:17:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Qual sobre minha estrutura?
Dialogue: 9,0:17:47.89,0:17:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,É óbvio que está perfeita.
Dialogue: 9,0:17:49.89,0:17:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Agora levanta!
Dialogue: 9,0:18:00.11,0:18:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Foi bom ele entrar no Mk. III.
Dialogue: 9,0:18:05.16,0:18:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Uau.
Dialogue: 9,0:18:07.58,0:18:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Não posso acreditar que não foi danificada\Naquele acidente.
Dialogue: 9,0:18:11.58,0:18:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,É incrível.
Dialogue: 9,0:18:13.13,0:18:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Parece exatamente com o Tsugumori Mk. II,\N
Dialogue: 9,0:18:15.50,0:18:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,mas por baixo, eles são completamente diferentes.
Dialogue: 9,0:18:19.30,0:18:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,A maioria dos módulos mais antigos\Nnão sobreviveu ao impacto.
Dialogue: 9,0:18:23.43,0:18:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Você pode agradecer aos novos materiais\Npelo seu resgate, Tanikaze.
Dialogue: 9,0:18:26.89,0:18:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Sua Tsugumori Mk. II\Nestaria por account de sucata agora.
Dialogue: 9,0:18:29.31,0:18:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 9,0:18:32.06,0:18:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,O barulho é bem forte.
Dialogue: 9,0:18:34.81,0:18:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,A atmosfera está\Ninterferindo com nosso link de comunicação.
Dialogue: 9,0:18:56.67,0:18:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumugi?
Dialogue: 9,0:18:57.84,0:18:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Onde você está?
