Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.34,0:22:35.43,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}Se este mundo estiver condenado à ruína,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.34,0:22:35.43,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,[T0][T1]aa kuchiteku sekai naraba
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.43,0:22:38.93,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}se minha vida estiver em perigo,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.43,0:22:38.93,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,[T0][T1]chiriyuku sadame naraba
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.02,0:22:44.52,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}então por que eu deveria viver?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.02,0:22:44.52,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,[T0][T1]nani wo shinjite ikireba ii
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.02,0:22:50.19,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}se não tivesse conhecido você,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.02,0:22:50.19,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,[T0][T1]sou kimi to deawanakereba
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.19,0:22:53.61,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}então eu nunca teria sentido este sofrimento
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.19,0:22:53.61,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}arrancando meu coração
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.78,0:23:00.25,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}quebrando meu coração ao meio
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.78,0:23:00.25,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}por não conhecer dor alguma
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.66,0:23:02.96,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}é uma requiem grosseira
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.66,0:23:02.96,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}no horizonte do céu
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.96,0:23:04.42,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}ecoando para
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.96,0:23:04.42,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}ressoou
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.42,0:23:08.25,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}as alturas do céu
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.42,0:23:08.25,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}um requiem inútil
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.25,0:23:10.17,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}e mesmo agora
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.25,0:23:10.17,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}mas ainda
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.17,0:23:11.88,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}neste mundo sem sentido
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.17,0:23:11.88,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}buscando
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.92,0:23:15.30,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}eu busco
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.92,0:23:15.30,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}um agora diferente
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.30,0:23:17.30,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}para você
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.30,0:23:17.30,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}o que é você
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.30,0:23:20.93,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}Eu me lembro
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.30,0:23:20.93,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}sosai shite ita yorokobi mo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.93,0:23:24.64,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}do prazer de te conhecer
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.93,0:23:24.64,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,[T0][T1]kieteitta nukumori mo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.64,0:23:28.90,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}e a passagem do seu estar aqui
